Package com.khalsa_ji.ems

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Designation
    The class Designation defines some useful properties for designations(Job titles) in any organisation, methods to play around with those defined properties and also acts as a database entity.
    Employee
    The class Employee defines various real world properties of an employee in any organisation, methods to play around with those defined properties and also acts as a database entity.
    EmployeeBrief
    The class EmployeeBrief defines some set of properties inspired from the Employee class.
    EmployeeChart
    The EmployeeChart class defines various properties of a typical employee information system/dashboard along with methods to play around with those properties.
    EMSApplication
    The class EMSApplication is declared as a Spring Boot Application class and provides a method as a main entry point for the application, Employee Management System.
    EMSApplicationTests
